Cogstate Battery Results

Source: R/data.R
CBBRESULTS.Rd

Cogstate Battery Results data. More information is available at https://adni.loni.usc.edu/data-samples/adni-data/

Usage

data(CBBRESULTS)

Format

A data frame with 22205 observations and 44 variables.

Source

https://adni.loni.usc.edu/data-samples/adni-data/

Details

  • ORIGPROT character Original study protocol , with options: ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI3

  • COLPROT character Study protocol of data collection , with options: ADNI2, ADNI3

  • RID numeric Participant roster ID Range value: 2, ..., 7125

  • SessionID numeric Range value: 2694, ..., 613669

  • EXAMDATE Examination Date Date: YYY-MM-DD

  • TestTime hms: HH-MM-SS

  • Visit character , with options: Remote, In Clinic, Unknown

  • SessionAttempt numeric Range value: 1, ..., 51

  • SessionDuration numeric Range value: 203, ..., 11907138

  • SessionCompletionPass character , with options: Yes, No

  • SessionPerformancePass character , with options: Yes, No

  • SessionIntegrityPass character , with options: Yes, No

  • TestCode character , with options: OneBack, Detection, Identification, OneCardLearning

  • TestAttempt numeric Range value: 1, ..., 3

  • TestCompletionScore numeric Range value: 72.5, ..., 300

  • TestPerformanceScore numeric Range value: 0, ..., 100

  • TestCompletionPass character , with options: Yes, No

  • TestPerformancePass character , with options: Yes, No

  • TestIntegrityPass character , with options: No, Yes

  • TestDuration numeric Range value: 31256, ..., 3782229

  • ReactionTime numeric Range value: 2.2601, ..., 3.9147

  • RawReactionTime numeric Range value: 182, ..., 23016.2308

  • RTVariability numeric Range value: 0.0194, ..., 0.7633

  • RawRTVariability numeric Range value: 12.7089, ..., 16932.8234

  • Accuracy numeric Range value: 0, ..., 1.5708

  • RawAccuracy numeric Range value: 0, ..., 1

  • TotalCorrect numeric Range value: 0, ..., 80

  • TotalCorrectExclPant numeric Range value: 0, ..., 80

  • TotalErrors numeric Range value: 0, ..., 110

  • LegalErrors numeric Range value: 0, ..., 89

  • RuleBreakErrors numeric Range value: 0, ..., 100

  • TotalAnticipatory numeric Range value: 0, ..., 80

  • TotalPost numeric Range value: 0, ..., 35

  • TotalMaxOut numeric Range value: 0, ..., 36

  • TotalResponses numeric Range value: 0, ..., 167

  • TotalTrials numeric Range value: 0, ..., 91

  • StandardScoreZ numeric Range value: -7.8207, ..., 4.8991

  • StandardScoreT numeric Range value: 21.793, ..., 148.9908

  • AltStandardScoreZ numeric Range value: -4.6389, ..., 2.7656

  • AltStandardScoreT numeric Range value: 53.6111, ..., 127.6564

  • Psyattstdscr numeric Range value: 37.6477, ..., 120.9856

  • LearnWMStdScr numeric Range value: 62.4325, ..., 137.4209

  • AltLearnWMStdScr numeric Range value: 46.8986, ..., 136.5113

  • update_stamp POSIXct: YYY-MM-DD
